## SEO Optimization Rules

### Semantic HTML5 Structure
- **Use semantic elements**: <header>, <nav>, <main>, <section>, <article>, <aside>, <footer>
- **Article tags**: Use <article> for standalone content blocks (testimonials, service descriptions, blog posts)
- **Section tags**: Use <section> for thematic groupings within the page
- **Main content**: Wrap primary content in <main> element
- **Navigation**: Use <nav> for all navigation elements
- **Header/Footer**: Use <header> and <footer> for page structure

### HTML5 Semantic Implementation
`html
<header>
